	window.RLQ.push(function() {
		function genUID() {
			const crypto = window['crypto'] || window['msCrypto'] || false;
			if (crypto && crypto.randomUUID) {
				return crypto.randomUUID();
			} else if (crypto && crypto.getRandomValues) {
				return ([1e7]+-1e3+-4e3+-8e3+-1e11).replace(/[018]/g, function(c) {
					return (c ^ crypto.getRandomValues(new Uint8Array(1))[0] & 15 >> c / 4).toString(16);
				});
			}

			return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function (c) {
				const r = Math.random() * 16 | 0, v = c === 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3 | 0x8);
				return v.toString(16);
			});
		}
		function getCookie(cookieName) {
			const cookieSplit = ('; ' + document.cookie).split('; ' + cookieName + '=');
			return cookieSplit.length === 2 ? cookieSplit.pop().split(';').shift() : null;
		}

			pvNumber: (parseInt(getCookie('pv_number'), 10) || 0) + 1,

      <div class="page-content" id="content">
       <script data-name="featured-video-mapped-to-wiki">
        (function () {
        // we can't use mw.config here because it's too early so we need to pass this data in different way
        var videoDetails = {
            mediaId: "K21eFFRc",
            impressionsPerSession: 3,
            isDedicatedForArticle: false,
            tier3Mapping: false,
        };
        var hasVideoOnPage = null;
        var videoBridgeCountries = ["US","GB","CA","AU","DE","SG","MY","VN","ID","PH","TH","ES","FR","AR","MX","CO","PE","NZ","IN","DE","VN","FR","BR","ES","PL","CL"];
        var tier3VideoBridgeCountries = ["MG","MX","AR"];

        function getCookieValue(cookieName) {
            var cookieSplit = ('; ' + document.cookie).split('; ' + cookieName + '=');
            return cookieSplit.length === 2 ? cookieSplit.pop().split(';').shift() : null;
        }

        function hasMaxedOutPlayerImpressionsInWiki() {
            var impressionsSoFar = Number(getCookieValue('playerImpressionsInWiki')) || 0;
            var allowedImpressions = Number(videoDetails.impressionsPerSession);

            if (!hasSeenTheVideoInCurrentSession()) {
                return false;
            }

            if (allowedImpressions === 0) {
                return true;
            }

            return impressionsSoFar >= allowedImpressions;
        }

        function hasSeenTheVideoInCurrentSession() {
            var currentSession = getCookieValue('wikia_session_id');
            var videoSeenInSession = getCookieValue('featuredVideoSeenInSession');

            return currentSession && videoSeenInSession && currentSession === videoSeenInSession;
        }

        function getCountryCode() {
            try {
                return JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(getCookieValue('Geo'))).country.toLowerCase();
            } catch {
                return null;
            }
        }

        function isVideoBridgeAllowedForCountry() {
            var countryCode = getCountryCode();
            // Check if the wikis is a tier3 wiki. This value comes back from the ArticleVideo service
            if (videoDetails && videoDetails.tier3Mapping) {
              // If the wiki is classified as a tier3 wiki, then check the country whitelist from the tier3VideoBridge whitelist.
              var allowedCountriesForTier3Wikis = tier3VideoBridgeCountries.map(function (allowedTier3CountryCode) {
                return allowedTier3CountryCode.toLowerCase();
              })

              return countryCode && allowedCountriesForTier3Wikis.indexOf(countryCode) !== -1;
            } else {
              // If not a tier3 wiki, then check the country whitelist from the videoBridge whitelist
              var allowedCountries = videoBridgeCountries.map(function (allowedCountryCode) {
                return allowedCountryCode.toLowerCase();
              });

              return countryCode && allowedCountries.indexOf(countryCode) !== -1;
            }
        }

        window.canPlayVideo = function () {
            if (hasVideoOnPage === null) {
                hasVideoOnPage = videoDetails.mediaId && (
                    videoDetails.isDedicatedForArticle ||
	                (!hasMaxedOutPlayerImpressionsInWiki() && isVideoBridgeAllowedForCountry())
                );
            }

            return hasVideoOnPage;
        };

        if (!window.canPlayVideo()) {
            document.body.classList.add('no-featured-video');
        } else {
	        document.body.classList.add('has-featured-video');
        }
    })();
       </script>

         <h2>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Movement">
           Movement
          </span>
         </h2>
         <h3>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="First_Move">
           First Move
          </span>
         </h3>
         <dl>
          <dt>
           First Move with an Enemy
           <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" data-champion="Pantheon" data-game="lol" data-param="" data-skin="Original" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
            <span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
             <a href="/wiki/Pantheon/LoL" title="Pantheon">
              <img alt="Pantheon" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-key="Pantheon_OriginalSquare.png" data-image-name="Pantheon OriginalSquare.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/03/Pantheon_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20190801100355" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
             </a>
            </span>
            <span style="white-space:normal;">
             <a href="/wiki/Pantheon/LoL" title="Pantheon/LoL">
              Pantheon
             </a>
            </span>
           </span>
          </dt>
         </dl>
         <ul>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/73/Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_0.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20201020232458" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_0.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_0.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_0.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original FirstMovePantheon 0.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="skin-play-button skinloading-icon" data-champion="Aatrox" data-skin="Original" data-variant="" style="position:relative; height:20px; width:20px; display:inline">
            <a class="image" href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9f/Aatrox_OriginalCircle.png/revision/latest?cb=20201218013448">
             <img alt="Aatrox OriginalCircle.png" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_OriginalCircle.png" data-image-name="Aatrox OriginalCircle.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9f/Aatrox_OriginalCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201218013448" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
            </a>
           </span>

             <img alt="Aatrox LunarEclipseCircle.png" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_LunarEclipseCircle.png" data-image-name="Aatrox LunarEclipseCircle.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/86/Aatrox_LunarEclipseCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220413013507" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
            </a>
           </span>
           <i>
            "Targon sends an aspect against me? Prepare yourself, Pantheon, I will end all that you hope to be!"
           </i>
          </li>
         </ul>

          <dt>
           Move Near Allies and Enemies (2v2 minimum) with
           <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" data-ability="World Ender" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">

             </a>
            </span>

           <i>
            "Am I challenged by a tree?! Fine, let me build a pyre from you!"

           <i>
            "You would end worlds? As a bow?!"

         <h3>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Using_Infernal_Chains">
           Using
           <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" data-ability="Infernal Chains" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
            <span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
             <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL#Infernal_Chains" title="Infernal Chains">
              <img alt="Infernal Chains" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_Infernal_Chains.png" data-image-name="Aatrox Infernal Chains.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/32/Aatrox_Infernal_Chains.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20210827172809" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
             </a>
            </span>
            <span style="white-space:normal;">
             <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL#Infernal_Chains" title="Aatrox/LoL">
              Infernal Chains
             </a>
            </span>
           </span>
          </span>
         </h3>

          <li>

         <h3>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Using_Umbral_Dash">
           Using
           <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" data-ability="Umbral Dash" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
            <span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
             <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL#Umbral_Dash" title="Umbral Dash">

          <dt>
           What
           <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" data-skin="Original" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">

         <h2>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Other_Gameplay">
           Other Gameplay
          </span>
         </h2>
         <dl>
          <dt>
           <span class="glossary" data-game="lol" data-tip="Resurrection" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;">
            <a href="/wiki/Death#Ways_to_prevent_death_when_reaching_zero_health" title="Death#Ways to prevent death when reaching zero health">

         <h2>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Unused">
           Unused
          </span>
         </h2>
         <dl>
          <dt>
           Enemy Flashing
           <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/Champion_mastery" title="Champion mastery">
            Mastery
           </a>
          </dt>
         </dl>
         <p>
          <b>
           NOTE:
          </b>
          On
          <a href="/wiki/V12.5" title="V12.5">
           12.5
          </a>
          , the following voicelines were entirely removed from the game without any explanation.
          <sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-1">
           <a href="#cite_note-1">
            [1]
           </a>
          </sup>
         </p>
         <p>
          <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Last checked: 13.6">
           <b>
            The voicelines still haven't been reimplemented.
           </b>
          </span>
         </p>

            <a class="image" href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/01/Aatrox_OdysseyCircle.png/revision/latest?cb=20201017001922">

            </a>
           </span>
           <i>
            "Mastery, how I idolise your greatness! Though I suspect your weapon lacks... impact."

         <h2>
          <span class="mw-headline" id="Trivia">
           Trivia
          </span>
         </h2>
         <dl>
          <dt>
           <span style="white-space:pre">
            <span class="inline-image label-after skin-icon" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" data-skin="Original" data-variant="old" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
             <span data-width="32" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
              <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics" title="Aatrox, the Darkin Blade">
               <img alt="Aatrox, the Darkin Blade" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_OriginalCircle_old.png" data-image-name="Aatrox OriginalCircle old.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d0/Aatrox_OriginalCircle_old.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/32?cb=20180613163659" decoding="async" height="32" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="32"/>
              </a>
             </span>
             <span style="white-space:normal;">
              <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics" title="Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics">
               Aatrox, the Darkin Blade
              </a>
             </span>
            </span>
           </span>
          </dt>
         </dl>
         <ul>
          <li>
           He shares a quote with:
           <ul>
            <li>
             <div class="audio-button">
              <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/74/Aatrox_Original_Attack_9_old.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20130520212542" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
               <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Attack_9_old.ogg">
                https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Attack_9_old.ogg
               </a>
              </audio>
             </div>
             <sup>
              <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Attack_9_old.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Attack 9 old.ogg">
              </a>
             </sup>
             <span class="skin-play-button skinloading-icon" data-champion="Aatrox" data-skin="Original" data-variant="old" style="position:relative; height:20px; width:20px; display:inline">
              <a class="image" href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d0/Aatrox_OriginalCircle_old.png/revision/latest?cb=20180613163659">
               <img alt="Aatrox OriginalCircle old.png" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_OriginalCircle_old.png" data-image-name="Aatrox OriginalCircle old.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d0/Aatrox_OriginalCircle_old.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180613163659" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
              </a>
             </span>
             <div class="audio-button">
              <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b5/LuxElementalist.Light.start01.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20161201213154" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
               <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:LuxElementalist.Light.start01.ogg">
                https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:LuxElementalist.Light.start01.ogg
               </a>
              </audio>
             </div>
             <sup>
              <a href="/wiki/File:LuxElementalist.Light.start01.ogg" title="File:LuxElementalist.Light.start01.ogg">
              </a>
             </sup>
             <span class="skin-play-button skinloading-icon" data-champion="Lux" data-skin="Elementalist" data-variant="" style="position:relative; height:20px; width:20px; display:inline">
              <a class="image" href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/13/Lux_ElementalistCircle.png/revision/latest?cb=20200618185308">
               <img alt="Lux ElementalistCircle.png" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Lux_ElementalistCircle.png" data-image-name="Lux ElementalistCircle.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/13/Lux_ElementalistCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200618185308" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
              </a>
             </span>
             <span class="template_sbc">
              <b>
               "Rage against the dying of the light."
              </b>
             </span>
             references
             <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Do_not_go_gentle_into_that_good_night" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
              Do not go gentle into that good night
             </a>
             by poet Dylan Thomas.
            </li>
           </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ed/Aatrox_Original_Move_9_old.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20130520212637" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_9_old.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_9_old.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_9_old.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Move 9 old.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "I know what lurks in the hearts of man."
            </b>
           </span>
           references
           <a class="external text" href="http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/The_Shadow" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            The Shadow
           </a>
           by
           <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_B._Gibson" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            Walter B. Gibson
           </a>
           (
           <i>
            "Who knows what evil lurks in the hearts of men? The Shadow knows... "
           </i>
           )
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cb/Aatrox_Original_Move_2_old.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20130520212636" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_2_old.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_2_old.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_2_old.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Move 2 old.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Peace is the greatest lie of all."
            </b>
           </span>
           might be referencing the
           <a class="extiw" href="https://starwars.fandom.com/wiki/Code_of_the_Sith" title="w:c:StarWars:Code of the Sith">
            Code of the Sith
           </a>
           from
           <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Wars" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            Star Wars
           </a>
           (
           <i>
            "Peace is a lie, there is only passion... "
           </i>
           )
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/08/Aatrox_Original_Taunt_4_old.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20130520212750" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Taunt_4_old.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Taunt_4_old.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Taunt_4_old.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Taunt 4 old.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Even those who have nothing can give their lives."
            </b>
           </span>
           might be referencing
           <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warhammer_40,000:_Dawn_of_War" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War
           </a>
           .
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8a/Aatrox_Original_Move_1_old.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20130520212635" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_1_old.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_1_old.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_1_old.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Move 1 old.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Pain is temporary, victory is forever."
            </b>
           </span>
           references
           <i>
            "Pain is temporary, pride is forever"
           </i>
           .
          </li>
          <li>
           Most of his taunts reference
           <i>
            "You either die a hero or you live long enough to see yourself become the villain"
           </i>
           .
          </li>
          <li>
           <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" data-ability="Massacre" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
            <span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
             <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL#Massacre" title="Massacre's">
              <img alt="Massacre's" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_Massacre.png" data-image-name="Aatrox Massacre.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/3b/Aatrox_Massacre.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170818000832" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
             </a>
            </span>
            <span style="white-space:normal;">
             <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL#Massacre" title="Aatrox/LoL">
              Massacre's
             </a>
            </span>
           </span>
           activation can be faintly heard anywhere on the map, with the voices speaking while active being Aatrox's voice-over lines
           <a class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCaXnG7y368" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            played in reverse
           </a>
           .

            <li>
             The roughtly translated speech has lines from his regular quotes, such as:

                 "Violence is elegance."
                </b>
               </span>
              </li>

                </b>
               </span>
              </li>
             </ul>
            </li>
           </ul>
          </li>
         </ul>
         <dl>
          <dt>
           <span style="white-space:pre">
            <span class="inline-image label-after skin-icon" data-champion="Aatrox" data-game="lol" data-param="" data-skin="Original" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
             <span data-width="32" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
              <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics" title="Original Aatrox">
               <img alt="Original Aatrox" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Aatrox_OriginalCircle.png" data-image-name="Aatrox OriginalCircle.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9f/Aatrox_OriginalCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/32?cb=20201218013448" decoding="async" height="32" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="32"/>
              </a>
             </span>
             <span style="white-space:normal;">
              <a href="/wiki/Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics" title="Aatrox/LoL/Cosmetics">
               Original Aatrox
              </a>
             </span>
            </span>
           </span>
          </dt>
         </dl>
         <ul>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/06/Aatrox_Original_Move_26.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20201020232714" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_26.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_26.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_Move_26.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original Move 26.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Am I the abyss? Or did I gaze into it?"
            </b>
           </span>
           references Friedrich Nietzsche's
           <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beyond_Good_and_Evil" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            Beyond Good and Evil
           </a>
           (
           <i>
            "He who fights with monsters should look to it that he himself does not become a monster. And if you gaze long into an abyss, the abyss also gazes into you."
           </i>
           )
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/01/Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20201020232414" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original FirstEncounterMalphite.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Where is your head,
             <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" data-champion="Malphite" data-game="lol" data-param="" data-skin="Original" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;">
              <span class="border" data-width="20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;">
               <a href="/wiki/Malphite/LoL" title="rock thing">
                <img alt="rock thing" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-key="Malphite_OriginalSquare.png" data-image-name="Malphite OriginalSquare.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Malphite_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220554" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
               </a>
              </span>
              <span style="white-space:normal;">
               <a href="/wiki/Malphite/LoL" title="Malphite/LoL">
                rock thing
               </a>
              </span>
             </span>
             ? Where is the neck I shall sever?"
            </b>
           </span>
           alludes to the notion that Malphite's head is hard to find on his in-game model.
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/ab/Aatrox_Original_KillNasus.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20201020232553" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_KillNasus.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_KillNasus.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_KillNasus.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original KillNasus.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Yes, Shurima was meant to fall, Nasus, as were you!"
            </b>
           </span>
           is a response to
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/96/Nasus_Original_Move_7.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20210601211400" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Nasus_Original_Move_7.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Nasus_Original_Move_7.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Nasus_Original_Move_7.ogg" title="File:Nasus Original Move 7.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="skin-play-button skinloading-icon" data-champion="Nasus" data-skin="Original" data-variant="" style="position:relative; height:20px; width:20px; display:inline">
            <a class="image" href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c6/Nasus_OriginalCircle.png/revision/latest?cb=20171112102112">
             <img alt="Nasus OriginalCircle.png" class="lazyload" data-image-key="Nasus_OriginalCircle.png" data-image-name="Nasus OriginalCircle.png" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c6/Nasus_OriginalCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171112102112" decoding="async" height="20" loading="lazy" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" width="20"/>
            </a>
           </span>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "Perhaps Shurima was meant to fall."
            </b>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <div class="audio-button">
            <audio controls="" preload="none" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/4d/Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_17.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20201020232800" style="max-width: 100%; width: 180px;" width="180">
             <a href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_17.ogg">
              https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_17.ogg
             </a>
            </audio>
           </div>
           <sup>
            <a href="/wiki/File:Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_17.ogg" title="File:Aatrox Original MoveLong 17.ogg">
            </a>
           </sup>
           <span class="template_sbc">
            <b>
             "No beast so fierce, but knows some touch of pity... But I know none... and therefore am no beast."
            </b>
           </span>
           references Lady Anne and Richard quotes in William Shakespeare's
           <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_III_(Shakespeare)" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
            Richard III
           </a>
           (
           <i>
            "Lady Anne: No beast so fierce but knows some touch of pity. / Richard: But I know none, and therefore am no beast."
           </i>
           )
          </li>
         </ul>
         <div style="clear:both">
         </div>
         <p>
          <br/>
         </p>

      <section class="global-footer__section global-footer__section-site-overview">
       <h3 class="global-footer__section-header">
        Overview
       </h3>
